40:19.418 --> 40:20.784
Have you?
[ chuckles ]

40:20.786 --> 40:22.519
Not that it's any
of my business.

40:23.454 --> 40:25.088
Well...

40:25.090 --> 40:26.723
Yeah.

40:26.725 --> 40:30.894
It's, uh...
It's kind of what I do.

40:36.734 --> 40:38.802
Cyrus: Oh, my god.

40:40.871 --> 40:43.873
Y-y-you're a, uh...

40:43.875 --> 40:45.809
"sex worker" I think

40:45.811 --> 40:49.012
Is the, uh, politically correct
term nowadays.

40:49.014 --> 40:50.914
[ chuckles ]

40:50.916 --> 40:52.649
[ sighs ]

40:52.651 --> 40:55.752
And while we're at it,
my name is michael.

40:55.754 --> 40:56.853
[ chuckles ]

40:56.855 --> 40:57.854
Right.

