¶ all the sweet,
green icing... ¶

41:21.580 --> 41:22.645
I...

41:22.647 --> 41:24.747
¶ ...Flowing down

41:24.749 --> 41:27.750
It's not that...At all.

41:27.752 --> 41:29.018
Well, then...

41:29.020 --> 41:31.120
¶ ...In the rain

41:31.122 --> 41:36.025
¶ I don't think
that I can take it ¶

41:36.027 --> 41:39.562
¶ 'cause it took so long
to bake it ¶

41:39.564 --> 41:42.065
¶ and I'll never have
that recipe... ¶

41:42.067 --> 41:43.700
...What's stopping you?

41:43.702 --> 41:46.703
